"title": "8662: meditation",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "8662",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Spending time in quietness and usually alone, drawing close to God and listening to him, pondering on his word, his creation, his mighty works or other aspects of his self-revelation.</p>\n<h2>The importance of meditation</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps1:1-Ps1:3\">PSA 1:1–1:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam12:24\">1SA 12:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job37:14\">JOB 37:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps19:14\">PSA 19:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps48:9\">PSA 48:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps77:11-Ps77:12\">PSA 77:11–77:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps104:34\">PSA 104:34</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps107:43\">PSA 107:43</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil4:8\">PHP 4:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim2:7\">2TI 2:7</a></p>\n<h2>Meditation on the person of God</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps16:8\">PSA 16:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps63:6\">PSA 63:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps104:34\">PSA 104:34</a></p>\n<h2>Meditation on God's word</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:15-Ps119:16\">PSA 119:15–119:16</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh1:8\">JOS 1:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps1:1-Ps1:3\">PSA 1:1–1:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:23\">PSA 119:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:48\">PSA 119:48</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:78\">PSA 119:78</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:95\">PSA 119:95</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:97\">PSA 119:97</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:99\">PSA 119:99</a></p>\n<h2>Meditation on the works of God</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps77:12\">PSA 77:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps111:2\">PSA 111:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps143:5\">PSA 143:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps145:5\">PSA 145:5</a></p>\n<h2>Meditation on the creation</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps8:1-Ps8:9\">PSA 8:1–8:9</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps104:1-Ps104:34\">PSA 104:1–104:34</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov6:6\">PRO 6:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt6:26-Matt6:30\">MAT 6:26–6:30</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke12:24-Luke12:27\">LUK 12:24–12:27</a></p>\n<h2>Meditation at night</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:148\">PSA 119:148</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps16:7\">PSA 16:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps42:8\">PSA 42:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps63:6\">PSA 63:6</a></p>\n<h2>Examples of people meditating</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh1:8\">JOS 1:8</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps19:14\">PSA 19:14</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job22:22\">JOB 22:22</a> <em>Eliphaz' advice to Job</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps39:3\">PSA 39:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:78\">PSA 119:78</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:148\">PSA 119:148</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke2:19\">LUK 2:19</a> <em>Mary</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts8:27-Acts8:35\">ACT 8:27–8:35</a> <em>the Ethiopian eunuch</em></p>\n<h2>The results of meditation</h2>\n<h3>Obedience</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:11\">PSA 119:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh1:8\">JOS 1:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:55\">PSA 119:55</a></p>\n<h3>Understanding and wisdom</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:97-Ps119:98\">PSA 119:97–119:98</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:27\">PSA 119:27</a></p>\n<h3>Praise and worship</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps48:9-Ps48:10\">PSA 48:9–48:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps63:5-Ps63:6\">PSA 63:5–63:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps104:33-Ps104:35\">PSA 104:33–104:35</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:97\">PSA 119:97</a></p>\n<h3>Prosperity and success</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh1:8\">JOS 1:8</a></strong></p>\n<h3>Delight in the LORD</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps1:2\">PSA 1:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:15-Ps119:16\">PSA 119:15–119:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:23-Ps119:24\">PSA 119:23–119:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:77-Ps119:78\">PSA 119:77–119:78</a></p>\n<h3>Confidence and faith</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps16:8\">PSA 16:8</a></strong></p>",
